ing: 4 cups Pepperidge FarmÂ® Cubed Country Style Stuffing
1 (10.75 ounce) can Campbell'sÂ® Condensed Cream of Chicken Soup (Regular or 98% Fat Free)
des: "Stuffing, chicken breasts, and cream of chicken soup bake together in this satisfying family meal."
ins:
Prepare stuffing according to pkg. directions.
Spoon stuffing across center of 3-qt. shallow baking dish.  Place chicken on each side of stuffing.  Sprinkle chicken with paprika.
Mix soup, milk and parsley.  Pour over chicken.  Cover.
Bake at 400 degrees F for 15 min.  Uncover and bake 15 min. or until chicken is done.
